name: iCloudFlare
tagline: iCloudFlare is a basic CloudFlare client. Currently a work-in-progress.
body:
### iCloudFlare
iCloudFlare is a work-in-progress CloudFlare management app for iOS. Eventual features will include the ability to view stats and update settings. iCloudFlare will be published for free on the app store once basic functionality and styling are complete. Feel free to fork or create issues in the tracker for any problems you see with my code.
